data.title: Invasion of the Astro-Monster (1970) - Popcorn Buckets
data.meta_description: Welcome astrologist, astronauts, and astronomers to Popcorn Buckets. Today we review the film Invasion of the Astro-Monsters (1970). The alien with the alias of Kyle rates it 2/10. The earthling Devin rates it 4.5/10. Grab your popcorn buckets and join us next week for our review of Godzilla vs. Hedorah (1971). 1. Website: https://therandomhour649452495.wordpress.com  2. Moore Sports: https://anchor.fm/devin-moore0 3. The Random Hour: https://anchor.fm/kyle-crump
